data.description: Charming Brick Home with an open floorplan and a wood-burning fireplace, perfect for cozy gatherings. The beautiful kitchen features marble countertops and a butcher block island. The spacious owner's suite offers a spa tub, sleek tile shower, and walk-in closet. Enjoy privacy in the fenced backyard and take advantage of the converted garage for added versatility. Located near Wintersmith Park and Mercy Hospital, this home offers a perfect blend of style and convenience!
